solution: ```class Solution {
public:
    int countSegments(string s) {
        int cnt = 0;
        bool inSegment = false;
        for (char c : s) {
            if (c != ' ') {
                if (!inSegment) {
                    cnt++;
                    inSegment = true;
                }
            } else {
                inSegment = false;
            }
        }
        return cnt;
    }
};
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Single pass through the string, counting each new non-space sequence. Constant extra space and minimal CPU usage.

